oning as the Executive Project Manager at the Bliss Services Limited, a Building and Civil Engineering firm. Adeleke is proficient in the use of Microsoft Office and Engineering software. Engineer Oloyede serves as an expert to the World Bank and Association of African Universities. He is a corporate member of the Nigerian Society of Engineers (NSE), Nigerian Institute of Civil Engineers (NICE) and Council for the Regulation of Engineering in Nigeria (COREN). As an Executive Director, he is the Chief Operation Officer of Shekelsfield Nigeria Limited saddles with the responsibilities of infrastructure, operations and logistics services. 
